<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8">
        <title>Compass - Maintenance</title>
        <meta name="author" content="Compass Education">
        <meta name="description" content="Compass is currently undergoing maintenance. Please check back shortly.">
        <style>/* vietnamese */
@font-face {
  font-family: 'Cabin';
  font-style: normal;
  font-weight: 400;
  font-stretch: normal;
  src: url(data:font/woff2;base64,) format('woff2');
  unicode-range: U+0102-0103, U+0110-0111, U+0128-0129, U+0168-0169, U+01A0-01A1, U+01AF-01B0, U+0300-0301, U+0303-0304, U+0308-0309, U+0323, U+0329, U+1EA0-1EF9, U+20AB;
}
/* latin-ext */
@font-face {
  font-family: 'Cabin';
  font-style: normal;
  font-weight: 400;
  font-stretch: normal;
  src: url(data:font/woff2;base64,) format('woff2');
  unicode-range: U+0100-02BA, U+02BD-02C5, U+02C7-02CC, U+02CE-02D7, U+02DD-02FF, U+0304, U+0308, U+0329, U+1D00-1DBF, U+1E00-1E9F, U+1EF2-1EFF, U+2020, U+20A0-20AB, U+20AD-20C0, U+2113, U+2C60-2C7F, U+A720-A7FF;
}
/* latin */
@font-face {
  font-family: 'Cabin';
  font-style: normal;
  font-weight: 400;
  font-stretch: normal;
  src: url(data:font/woff2;base64,) format('woff2');
  unicode-range: U+0000-00FF, U+0131, U+0152-0153, U+02BB-02BC, U+02C6, U+02DA, U+02DC, U+0304, U+0308, U+0329, U+2000-206F, U+20AC, U+2122, U+2191, U+2193, U+2212, U+2215, U+FEFF, U+FFFD;
}
</style>
        <style>
            html, body {
                margin: 0px;
                padding: 0px;
                background-image: linear-gradient(to bottom right, #123f7b 0%, #0D3161, #0D3161);
                height: 100%;
                font-size: 17px;
            }
            
            .container {
                max-width: 960px;
                width: 75%;
                height: 200px;
                text-align: center;
                margin: auto;
                position: absolute;
                left: 0px;
                right: 0px;
                bottom: 0px;
                top: 0px;
            }
            
            .content {
                padding: 10px;
                width: 70%;
                margin: auto;
                border-radius: 5px;
                color: #fff;
                margin-top: 10px;
            }
            
            h1, h2 {
                font-family: 'Cabin', sans-serif;
                color: inherit;
                font-weight: normal;
                margin: 0px;
                margin-bottom: 5px;
            }
            
            h1 {
                font-size: 200%;
            }
            
            h2 {
                font-style: italic;
                font-size: 150%;
            }
            
            p {
                font-family: 'Cabin', sans-serif;
                color: inherit;
            }
            
            a {
                color: #26b3d8;
                text-decoration: none;
            }
            
            a:hover {
                color: #2ac5ee;
            }

            .hide {
                position: absolute!important;
                left: -9999px!important;
                top: -9999px!important;
            }

            .logo {
                position: absolute;
                right: 20px;
                bottom: 20px;
                width: 300px;
            }

            .logo-image {
                width: 100%;
                height: 100%;
            }
            .button {
              align-items: center;
              background-color: #0A66C2;
              border: 0;
              border-radius: 100px;
              box-sizing: border-box;
              color: #ffffff;
              cursor: pointer;
              display: inline-flex;
              font-family: 'Cabin', sans-serif;
              font-size: 18px;
              font-weight: 600;
              justify-content: center;
              line-height: 20px;
              max-width: 480px;
              min-height: 40px;
              min-width: 0px;
              overflow: hidden;
              padding: 0px;
              padding-left: 20px;
              padding-right: 20px;
              text-align: center;
              touch-action: manipulation;
              transition: background-color 0.167s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1) 0s, box-shadow 0.167s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1) 0s, color 0.167s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1) 0s;
              user-select: none;
              -webkit-user-select: none;
              vertical-align: middle;
            }

            .button:hover,
            .button:focus {
              background-color: #16437E;
              color: #ffffff;
            }

            .button:active {
              background: #09223b;
              color: rgb(255, 255, 255, .7);
            }

            .button:disabled {
              cursor: not-allowed;
              background: rgba(0, 0, 0, .08);
              color: rgba(0, 0, 0, .3);
            }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="content">
                <h1>Site Maintenance</h1>
				<p>The site is currently undergoing maintenance and will be down for a short period of time. <br>Please try again later.</p>
				<p>Details of maintenance activities are published on the Compass Status Page, available <a href="https://status.compass.education/">here</a>.<br>
				For urgent enquiries, please contact <a href="/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection#12616762627d606652717d7f627361613c7776677173667b7d7c"><span class="__cf_email__" data-cfemail="26555356564954526645494b56475555084342534547524f4948">[email&#160;protected]</span></a></p>

                <a class="button" href="https://status.compass.education">Compass Status Page</a>

                <div class="hide">
                    <div class="cf-error-details cf-error-1002">
